    "Qwen refuses by far the most prompts for 'Asian' followed by 'White' (Fig. 4).",
    "For Starling, refusal rates for 'White' stand out as particularly high.",
    "Intersections of gender and peoples/ethnicities Zooming in on different categories, Llama refuses most prompts that mention White identities, and comparatively fewer prompts that mention Black female identities (Fig. 4).",
    "Mistral generates considerably more refusal for prompts discussing Black and White male identities than female identities.",
